               <p>FIFTH DAY. TUESDAY, DECEMBER 11.</p>
               <p>Third London Jury - before Mr. Common Sergeant.</p>
               <p>218. 
               <persName id="t18271206-217-defend1175" type="defendantName">
                  JOHN 
                  MEDENS
               <interp inst="t18271206-217-defend1175" type="surname" value="MEDENS"></interp>
